<!-- CLIENT ONBOARDING FLOW -->
<div class="section" id="client-flow">
  <div class="section-tag">Section 02</div>
  <h2>Client <em>Onboarding Flow</em></h2>
  <p>Step-by-step process from lead to live bot — target: complete in under 48 hours.</p>

  <div class="flow-grid">
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 01</div>
      <h4>🤝 Sales Call</h4>
      <p>Understand business type, products/services, customer base, goals. Decide pricing plan.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">30 mins</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 02</div>
      <h4>📋 Onboarding Form</h4>
      <p>Client fills Google Form: Business name, WhatsApp number, products, FAQs, support hours, tone.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">Client does — 15 mins</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 03</div>
      <h4>💳 Payment</h4>
      <p>Razorpay link send. Payment confirm ஆனா setup start. No payment = no setup.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">Instant</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 04</div>
      <h4>📱 WhatsApp Setup</h4>
      <p>Client's number Meta Business-ல add. Webhook configure. Permanent token generate.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">2-4 hours</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 05</div>
      <h4>🤖 Bot Configuration</h4>
      <p>System prompt write — business name, products, tone, language. Knowledge Base feed பண்ணு.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">1-2 hours</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 06</div>
      <h4>🧪 Testing</h4>
      <p>10+ test messages. Tamil + English. Product queries, greetings, out-of-scope. Fix issues.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">30 mins</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 07</div>
      <h4>🚀 Go Live</h4>
      <p>Client dashboard access give. Training video/doc share. Bot live announcement.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">15 mins</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-card">
      <div class="flow-step">STEP 08</div>
      <h4>📊 Monthly Review</h4>
      <p>Message stats, customer engagement report. Bot update if needed. Renewal reminder.</p>
      <span class="flow-time">Monthly — 30 mins</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- AI SETUP PER CLIENT -->
<div class="section" id="ai-setup">
  <div class="section-tag">Section 03</div>
  <h2>AI Setup <em>Per Client</em></h2>
  <p>How to configure Afi bot for different businesses — what data to collect and how to feed it.</p>

  <table class="ai-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Data Type</th>
        <th>What to Collect</th>
        <th>How to Get It</th>
        <th>Where It Goes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Business Info</td>
        <td>Name, location, hours, contact, website</td>
        <td>Onboarding form</td>
        <td>System Prompt</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Products/Services</td>
        <td>Name, price, description, variants, availability</td>
        <td>Form / WhatsApp catalog / website scrape</td>
        <td>Knowledge Base → Products</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Policies</td>
        <td>Refund, shipping, exchange, warranty</td>
        <td>Onboarding form</td>
        <td>Knowledge Base → Policies</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>FAQs</td>
        <td>Top 10 customer questions + answers</td>
        <td>Client interview / past chat history</td>
        <td>Knowledge Base → FAQs</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Tone/Language</td>
        <td>Formal/casual, Tamil/English/both, brand voice</td>
        <td>Onboarding form</td>
        <td>System Prompt</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Bot Persona</td>
        <td>Bot name, role (support/sales/both)</td>
        <td>Client decision</td>
        <td>System Prompt</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Escalation</td>
        <td>When to hand off to human, who to contact</td>
        <td>Onboarding form</td>
        <td>System Prompt</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
