    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">1</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Receive Onboarding Form</h4>
        <p>Client fills Google Form. Auto-save to Google Sheet. Check all fields are complete. If missing — WhatsApp client immediately.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 0 — 15 mins</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">2</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Collect Payment</h4>
        <p>Send Razorpay link via WhatsApp. Confirm payment received. Create client record in your management sheet.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 0 — Instant</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">3</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Meta Setup — Add Client Number</h4>
        <p>Go to Meta Business Manager → WhatsApp → Add Phone Number. Client verifies their number via OTP. Generate permanent system token.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 1 — 1-2 hours</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">4</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Create Bot in Dashboard</h4>
        <p>Go to GoGadAFI Dashboard → Bot Manager → Add New Bot. Fill: Name, System Prompt (using template + client data), set as active.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 1 — 30 mins</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">5</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Feed Knowledge Base</h4>
        <p>Dashboard → Knowledge Base → Select bot → Add products, policies, FAQs from onboarding form. Save. Test immediately.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 1 — 45 mins</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">6</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Configure Webhook for Client Number</h4>
        <p>In server.js — add client's PHONE_NUMBER_ID and TOKEN as environment variable OR create separate Railway service per client.</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 1 — 1 hour</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">7</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Test — 10 Message Checklist</h4>
        <p>✓ Greeting (Hi/Hello) ✓ Product query ✓ Price query ✓ Out-of-scope ✓ Tamil message ✓ English message ✓ Policy query ✓ Escalation trigger ✓ First-time welcome ✓ Return customer</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 1 — 30 mins</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sop-item">
      <div class="sop-num">8</div>
      <div class="sop-content">
        <h4>Handover to Client</h4>
        <p>Send welcome email/WhatsApp with: Dashboard login, bot live confirmation, how-to guide PDF, support contact. Done!</p>
        <div class="sop-time">⏱ Day 2 — 15 mins</div>
